  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK180">
<l>iṟalīṉu meṇṇātu veḵkiṉ viṟalīṉum</l>
<l>vēṇṭāmai yeṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To covet (the wealth of another) regardless of consequences will bring destruction. That greatness (of mind) which covets not will give victory.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
